These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
5 different games are played: whist, scrabble, bridge, billiard, backgammon
There are 5 different nationalities: british, argentine, american, polish, mexican
1. the polish is in an odd position##4
2. the polish is in the middle##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the british##3
4. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person playing whist is between the polish and the american##2
6. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
7. the polish is on the right of the mexican##1
8. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Game          | scrabble | whist | backgammon | billiard | bridge |
| Nationality   | american  | mexican      | polish   | british     | argentine    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: september, august, march, december, july
There are 5 different nationalities: canadian, pakistani, dutch, argentine, brazilian
1. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the argentine##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
4. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
5. the canadian is between the person who's birthday is in march and the argentine##2
6. the dutch is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Birthday   | march     | december       | july    | september | august   |
| Nationality      | pakistani | canadian | argentine | brazilian      | dutch |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: satire, zombie, musical, scientific, martial-arts
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, almond-milk, water, cola
1. the person drinking water is the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
7. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| Movie-Genre         | satire | musical | zombie | scientific    | martial-arts |
| Beverage   | water     | fanta        | almond-milk      | iced-tea | cola      |

