.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
There 5 different types of food: raspberry, grapefruit, grapes, peas, pumpkin
The people use 5 different means of transport: skateboard, train, roller, airplane, boat
1. the person eating grapes is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is the person driving the train##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is between the person driving the roller and the person eating pumpkin##2
7. the person driving the boat is the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Food         | raspberry      | peas | grapes | grapefruit   | pumpkin  |
| Transport   | airplane | boat    | roller        | skateboard | train |

