.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
City: rome, edinburgh, venice, colone, prague
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: thriller, zombie, time-travel, action, superhero
1. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
5. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
6. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
7. the person watching zombie movies is in an even position##4
8. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| City      | prague      | edinburgh | rome   | colone  | venice  |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | action | thriller | zombie | superhero |

