.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: snowmobile, taxi, train, bike, boat
5 different pets are kept: hamster, guinea-pig, rat, frog, fish
1. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the fish and the person driving the train##2
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the train is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the owner of the rat is the person driving the train##1
6. the owner of the rat is in an even position##4
7. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
8. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Transport   | taxi        | snowmobile                | bike  | train  | boat            |
| Pet        | hamster | fish | guinea-pig | rat | frog |

