.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
5 different pets are kept: turtle, lizard, bird, frog, rat
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, fonseca, dannemann, blend, chaman
1. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
2. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
3. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the dannemann-smoker is in an odd position##4
6. the owner of the turtle is on the far right##1
7. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
8. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
9. the blend-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Pet   | rat       | bird   | lizard    | frog    | turtle |
| Cigar        | dannemann | baccarat | fonseca | chaman | blend     |

