.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, fonseca, dannemann, siglo, bolivar
The people have 5 different hobbies: chess, fishing, woodworking, writing, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
2. the siglo-smoker is the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is the siglo-smoker##1
4. the siglo-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the fonseca-smoker is the person who's hobby is chess##1
6. the dannemann-smoker is between the fonseca-smoker and the tiparillo-smoker##2
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Cigar   | bolivar | fonseca | dannemann     | tiparillo | siglo |
| Hobby           | fishing | chess     | woodworking | video-games    | writing      |

