5 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, snooker, chess, poker
1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who likes black##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person playing backgammon is the person who likes yellow##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
5. the person playing chess is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
7. the person who likes brown is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |      3      |     4      |    5    |
| Color     | black | blood-red | brown | yellow | apricot |
| Game   | snooker | poker | chess    | backgammon    | mah-jongg  |

