.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, september, july, june, november
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, spy, epic, time-travel
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is in the middle##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person watching family movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person who's birthday is in september##2
7. the person watching fantasy movies is in an odd position##4
8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
9. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Birthday        | june | november | august  | july | september     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | spy     | time-travel | family      | epic |

