.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-13::.
5 different games are played: go, monopoly, poker, mah-jongg, backgammon
The people use 5 different means of transport: snowmobile, jet-ski, motorbike, van, tram
1. the person playing mah-jongg is in an even position##4
2. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
3. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
6. the person playing monopoly is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person playing poker##2
7. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
8. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| Game      | backgammon       | poker | monopoly | mah-jongg   | go   |
| Transport   | van | jet-ski | tram  | snowmobile | motorbike |

