3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating radish##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
6. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person eating avocado##3
7. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
8. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
9. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
