.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-18::.
5 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, domino, mah-jongg, scrabble
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: handball, baseball, rugby, parkour, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
5. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
8. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing domino##1
9. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5      |
| Game   | monopoly | snooker | scrabble     | domino | mah-jongg |
| Sport     | parkour       | baseball   | rugby | handball   | water-polo        |

