.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-19::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, cycling, skiing, biathlon, surfing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, martial-arts, superhero, family, time-travel
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching superhero movies is the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
5. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person watching time-travel movies##2
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person watching time-travel movies##2
7. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
8. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Sport         | biathlon | skiing | cycling | surfing | swimming     |
| Movie-Genre   | family    | martial-arts   | time-travel       | superhero | adventure |

