.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
5 different games are played: billiard, bridge, mah-jongg, monopoly, go
House: modern, townhouse, victorian, futuristic, cottage
1. the futuristic house is on the left of the person playing go##1
2. the victorian house is on the right of the person playing go##1
3. the townhouse house is between the cottage house and the futuristic house##2
4. the victorian house is on the right of the person playing go##1
5. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1
6. the cottage house is the person playing billiard##1
7. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Game   | billiard | mah-jongg      | monopoly | go     | bridge      |
| House     | cottage | townhouse | futuristic | modern | victorian |

 